<Sect2 Id="ToSelectAWindowOrIconKB">
<Title>To Select a Window or Icon</Title>
<IndexTerm>
<Primary>selecting: windows, with keyboard</Primary>
</IndexTerm>
<IndexTerm>
<Primary>keyboard: selecting windows and icons</Primary>
</IndexTerm>
<IndexTerm>
<Primary>window: selecting keyboard</Primary>
</IndexTerm>
<ItemizedList Mark="&bull;">
<ListItem Id="HIMGR.KEYB.item.40">
<Para>Press Alt+Tab to move the highlight to the window or icon
you want to select.</Para>
<Para>When a window or icon is selected, its border changes color to show that it
is active and will receive input from the mouse or keyboard.
</Para>
</ListItem>
</ItemizedList>
<Procedure>
<Title>See Also</Title>
